title: Resource® 2.0
field_ons_description: RESOURCE® 2.0 is a great tasting nutrient dense supplement. It is nutritionally formulated for the dietary management of individuals with unintended weight loss, malnutrition, for those requiring wound healing or are fluid restricted/volume sensitive

title: Resource® HP/HC
field_ons_description: RESOURCE® HP/HC is a high-protein, high energy supplement specifically formulated for those with an elevated need for protein and calories

title: Resource® Senior Activ
field_ons_description: RESOURCE® SeniorActiv is specifically formulated to target the nutritional needs of the elderly when they require increased energy and strength, such as following a fall or fracture or for the management of undernutrition and frailty

title: Resource® Protein
field_ons_description: RESOURCE® Protein is a high protein supplement specifically formulated for those with additional protein requirements

title: Resource® Support Plus
field_ons_description: RESOURCE® Support Plus is a high protein, high-calorie supplement specifically formulated for the increased nutritional needs of cancer/oncology patients

title: Resource® Repair
field_ons_description: Resource® Repair is for the dietary management of patients with malnutrition or at risk of malnutrition and with wounds and difficult wound healing.

title: Resource® ThickenUp Clear
field_ons_description: Resource® ThickenUp® Clear is a powder thickener used to modify the consistency of food and drink, both hot and cold, without changing the flavor or color.

title: Resource® Fruit
field_ons_description: Resource® Fruit is for the dietary management of patients with malnutrition or at risk of malnutrition.
